1
00:00:05,960 --> 00:00:08,660
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,660 --> 00:00:12,115
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,115 --> 00:00:18,215
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,215 --> 00:00:24,441
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,441 --> 00:00:31,062
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,062 --> 00:00:36,048
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:36,048 --> 00:00:43,348
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,348 --> 00:00:48,360
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,360 --> 00:00:49,885
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,885 --> 00:00:55,600
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,600 --> 00:01:00,600
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:07,400
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,072 --> 00:01:11,859
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:11,859 --> 00:01:16,580
[Tie Yuan Train Station]

15
00:01:16,580 --> 00:01:18,560
[Security Department]

16
00:01:30,440 --> 00:01:32,863
Does it hurt?

17
00:01:32,863 --> 00:01:35,800
Now you're pretending to be the good guy when you were the one that just chased me.

18
00:01:35,800 --> 00:01:37,700
If you didn't run, would I have chased you?

19
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:39,799
You bumped your face yourself. Are you blaming me?

20
00:01:39,799 --> 00:01:41,439
If you hadn't chased me, would I have run?

21
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,959
If I hadn't run, would I have bumped into something?

22
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,549
Just because you're young, you think you can run away from home?

23
00:01:44,549 --> 00:01:46,320
Don't you know why I ran away, huh?

24
00:01:46,320 --> 00:01:49,260
Well, tell me why you ran away.

25
00:01:58,842 --> 00:02:00,580
- Your name?
- Gao Bin.

26
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,420
- Age?
- Forty-three.

27
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:04,846
- Where do you work?
- Tian Yuan High School 3.

28
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,060
Comrade, well...

29
00:02:08,060 --> 00:02:09,907
Is it necessary to notify my employer?

30
00:02:09,907 --> 00:02:12,460
You tell me if it's necessary? What were you thinking?

31
00:02:12,460 --> 00:02:14,039
The train is not your home!

32
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:16,872
Didn't you realize fighting on the train would disturb other passengers?

33
00:02:16,872 --> 00:02:19,460
Look at the way you left that compartment. It's a huge mess!

34
00:02:19,460 --> 00:02:21,340
The other passengers all fled in terror!

35
00:02:21,340 --> 00:02:23,481
It was all his fault.

36
00:02:23,481 --> 00:02:24,952
Go on.

37
00:02:26,180 --> 00:02:28,700
I'm a PE teacher at Tian Yuan High School 3.

38
00:02:28,700 --> 00:02:30,346
I'm just an honest man.

39
00:02:30,346 --> 00:02:32,360
If it wasn't for this rotten kid,

40
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:36,252
I would never cause any trouble for the railway station.

41
00:02:36,252 --> 00:02:37,585
What's your relationship?

42
00:02:37,585 --> 00:02:39,349
- I don't know him.
- He's my son.

43
00:02:40,703 --> 00:02:42,990
You don't know me?

44
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:45,784
Station Manager, just look how handsome I am.

45
00:02:45,784 --> 00:02:47,403
How could I be his son?

46
00:02:47,403 --> 00:02:49,357
Look at him.

47
00:02:51,220 --> 00:02:54,620
You're making me laugh.

48
00:02:54,620 --> 00:02:56,104
You don't know me, right?

49
00:02:56,104 --> 00:02:59,391
Fine. Let's get to know each other today.

50
00:02:59,391 --> 00:03:00,604
Comrade,

51
00:03:00,604 --> 00:03:02,504
his name is Gao Yang.

52
00:03:02,504 --> 00:03:03,683
He's seventeen years old,

53
00:03:03,683 --> 00:03:05,715
a Sophomore in Class Three of Tian Yuan High School 3.

54
00:03:05,715 --> 00:03:07,677
His grade was third from the last in the previous semester.

55
00:03:07,677 --> 00:03:08,926
He had a crush on Wang Cailing in his class.

56
00:03:08,926 --> 00:03:11,660
Wang Cailing even moved to Beijing to avoid him. He thought I didn't know.

57
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:13,175
She wasn't avoiding me.

58
00:03:13,175 --> 00:03:16,740
Look. Look, Comrade. He slipped.

59
00:03:16,740 --> 00:03:18,280
Do you know me now?

60
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,420
Station Manager, yes, he's my father.

61
00:03:20,420 --> 00:03:23,324
But I no longer recognize our father and son relationship.

62
00:03:23,324 --> 00:03:24,540
Look at my wound.

63
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,780
He did that.

64
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,743
I've raised you for 17 years in vain? Ungrateful child!

65
00:03:27,743 --> 00:03:31,564
- You used my mom's money to raise me for 17 years! You say you raised me?
- Well, she... she did give you some...

66
00:03:31,564 --> 00:03:33,303
All right, enough!

67
00:03:33,303 --> 00:03:35,023
Stop screaming at each other here.

68
00:03:35,023 --> 00:03:37,100
If you are his father, you have the greater responsibility.

69
00:03:37,100 --> 00:03:38,644
How did you educate your son?

70
00:03:38,644 --> 00:03:40,187
Come on,

71
00:03:40,187 --> 00:03:41,540
tell me what happened

72
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:43,979
from start to finish.

73
00:03:44,570 --> 00:03:46,840
[Tieyuan, Beijing]

74
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:49,296
[Episode 1: The "Naughty" Boy]

75
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,800
Hello. Jiabao.

76
00:03:54,800 --> 00:03:56,803
This is Gao Yang.

77
00:03:56,803 --> 00:03:58,350
What?

78
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:02,003
I... Right now, I'm on...

79
00:04:02,003 --> 00:04:04,006
a train to Beijing right now.

80
00:04:04,006 --> 00:04:06,325
I'm saying goodbye to Tieyuan.

81
00:04:08,143 --> 00:04:09,500
Don't worry about the money.

82
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:11,662
I'll surely pay you back.

83
00:04:17,104 --> 00:04:20,000
Why is Gao Bin here? Which one of you sold me out?

84
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:23,863
Excuse me, Sir. Have you seen a 17-year-old boy?

85
00:04:23,863 --> 00:04:27,235
He's about this tall and wearing a pair of white sneakers.

86
00:04:27,235 --> 00:04:29,483
- No.
- Hello?

87
00:04:29,483 --> 00:04:30,949
Hello?

88
00:04:33,134 --> 00:04:35,280
Which compartment do you belong to?

89
00:04:35,280 --> 00:04:37,079
Where's your ticket?

90
00:04:43,664 --> 00:04:44,904
Hurry up.

91
00:04:44,904 --> 00:04:46,604
Gao Yang?

92
00:04:46,604 --> 00:04:48,104
Stop!

93
00:04:48,104 --> 00:04:49,523
Stop right there!

94
00:04:49,523 --> 00:04:51,925
Stop!

95
00:04:53,004 --> 00:04:54,856
Stop!

96
00:04:56,483 --> 00:04:58,037
Stop!

97
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,283
Stop!

98
00:05:00,283 --> 00:05:02,225
Gao Yang, stop running!

99
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:24,640
Get off the train!

100
00:05:24,640 --> 00:05:26,580
I want to go to Beijing!

101
00:05:26,580 --> 00:05:27,740
As long as I'm here,

102
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:29,800
don't you try to leave Tieyuan!

103
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:31,880
In your dreams!

104
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:34,200
Get off the train!

105
00:05:35,990 --> 00:05:39,430
The Spring breeze and rain...

106
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:42,884
confirm it is Spring Season in Tieyuan.

107
00:05:42,884 --> 00:05:47,400
The 2008 Beijing Olympic Games will be arriving in three years.

108
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:52,320
We should swim and thrive in the sea of knowledge,

109
00:05:52,320 --> 00:05:56,180
become a pillar for our motherland, and an outstanding talent for the world

110
00:05:56,180 --> 00:05:57,760
to make our contributions to the Beijing Olympic Games as soon as possible.

111
00:05:57,760 --> 00:05:59,764
♪ I love Tiananmen in Beijing ♪

112
00:05:59,764 --> 00:06:02,740
♪ The sun rises over Tiananmen ♪

113
00:06:02,740 --> 00:06:05,564
Gao Yang, you're not going to Beijing to watch the flag-raising ceremony?

114
00:06:05,564 --> 00:06:07,140
What's so interesting about the flag-raising ceremony?

115
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,919
You even have to line up for that.

116
00:06:08,919 --> 00:06:11,224
Since you're not going,

117
00:06:11,224 --> 00:06:12,180
pay me back now.

118
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,860
- Why are you in such a hurry?
- Give it back.

119
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:15,644
I don't have money. Stop feeling around!

120
00:06:15,644 --> 00:06:17,144
So annoying.

121
00:06:17,984 --> 00:06:19,898
Your dad hit you?

122
00:06:20,423 --> 00:06:22,101
I bumped it myself.

123
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,464
Are you still going to Beijing or not?

124
00:06:24,464 --> 00:06:26,943
I'll certainly go to Beijing,

125
00:06:26,943 --> 00:06:29,429
but I have to take some time to consider it.

126
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:32,823
Are you reluctant to leave me?

127
00:06:32,823 --> 00:06:34,540
Gao Yang!

128
00:06:34,540 --> 00:06:36,760
You must be reluctant to leave me.

129
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:38,718
Do you want some milk ice cream?

130
00:06:44,430 --> 00:06:45,514
It hurts!

131
00:06:45,514 --> 00:06:47,231
Oh my God, Gao Yang!

132
00:06:47,231 --> 00:06:49,780
Did Uncle Gao really hit you?

133
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:51,664
If I knew Uncle Gao would hit you so hard,

134
00:06:51,664 --> 00:06:53,403
I would never tell him.

135
00:06:53,403 --> 00:06:55,345
Beibei.

136
00:06:57,363 --> 00:06:59,383
- Jin Beibei!
- Meng!

137
00:06:59,383 --> 00:07:01,780
It was you? How could you do that?

138
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:02,860
What are you doing?

139
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:04,500
Time for class.

140
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:06,900
I'll handle you after class.

141
00:07:06,900 --> 00:07:08,420
What just happened?

142
00:07:08,420 --> 00:07:10,124
I told on him.

143
00:07:10,124 --> 00:07:12,456
You're still smiling?

144
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,380
Isn't that Gao Yang?

145
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,823
Why? You're not going to Beijing?

146
00:07:22,823 --> 00:07:25,444
Gao Yang can't bear to leave us.

147
00:07:25,444 --> 00:07:28,299
That's right. Well, I'm mainly reluctant to leave you, Mr. Wu.

148
00:07:28,299 --> 00:07:29,540
I miss you so much.

149
00:07:29,540 --> 00:07:31,781
Thank you.

150
00:07:31,781 --> 00:07:33,360
What's this? I see that you've paid for your actions.

151
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,344
It's nothing.

152
00:07:34,344 --> 00:07:37,263
Fine, it's okay if you don't go to Beijing. Just stay here and study diligently.

153
00:07:37,263 --> 00:07:39,224
Make up for the homework you missed.

154
00:07:39,224 --> 00:07:41,104
- Zhao Jiabao, do my homework for me.
- No.

155
00:07:41,104 --> 00:07:42,540
Ask him for it.

156
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:46,423
By the way, Tian Meng, come here. Distribute this to everyone after class.

157
00:07:46,423 --> 00:07:48,204
This is a classmate of Wang Cailing's.

158
00:07:48,204 --> 00:07:50,819
Wang Cailing sent you a postcard from Beijing.

159
00:07:50,819 --> 00:07:51,940
Look,

160
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:53,421
this means she's still thinking about her classmates

161
00:07:53,421 --> 00:07:55,943
from thousands of miles away. She's very affectionate towards you.

162
00:07:55,943 --> 00:07:57,633
All right, let's start class.

163
00:07:58,765 --> 00:08:00,302
Beibei.

164
00:08:01,175 --> 00:08:01,920
Beibei.

165
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,124
What?

166
00:08:03,124 --> 00:08:05,036
See if there's one for me.

167
00:08:11,163 --> 00:08:12,594
No.

168
00:08:13,244 --> 00:08:15,829
- She already forgot you.
- Go away.

169
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:18,844
It's all gone with the wind.

170
00:09:08,960 --> 00:09:11,440
What are you doing, Gao Bin? It never ends, does it?

171
00:09:11,440 --> 00:09:12,684
What do you think I'm doing?

172
00:09:12,684 --> 00:09:15,064
Come on. Hit me right here. Come on. Come on.

173
00:09:15,064 --> 00:09:16,760
- What else can you do besides hit me?
- Go away!

174
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:19,100
- Hit me, hit me!
- Go away!

175
00:09:19,100 --> 00:09:21,110
Childish.

176
00:09:27,705 --> 00:09:30,491
What are you doing? Conducting research?

177
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:33,040
Making dumplings.

178
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:34,680
Do you know how?

179
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:37,040
I can always learn.

180
00:09:37,040 --> 00:09:38,320
It's been over ten years

181
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,313
and you're finally learning it now?

182
00:09:41,820 --> 00:09:44,641
Just wait to eat it, what's with the nonsense?

183
00:09:44,641 --> 00:09:46,576
Is it edible?

184
00:09:49,146 --> 00:09:51,507
Worse comes to worst, it'll be pancakes.

185
00:09:59,785 --> 00:10:01,325
Can you do it or not?

186
00:10:01,325 --> 00:10:03,773
Otherwise, I'm going upstairs for dinner.

187
00:10:06,126 --> 00:10:08,181
Hurry up.

188
00:10:11,685 --> 00:10:13,907
You actually did it.

189
00:10:15,566 --> 00:10:17,560
What is this?

190
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,920
It used to be dumplings, but now

191
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,417
it's dough wrappers and meat.

192
00:10:22,417 --> 00:10:24,926
You eat the meat and I'll eat the dough wrappers, okay?

193
00:10:24,926 --> 00:10:26,866
Besides,

194
00:10:26,866 --> 00:10:29,286
taste is more important than shape for dumplings.

195
00:10:29,286 --> 00:10:30,981
Try one, it's delicious.

196
00:10:30,981 --> 00:10:33,079
Try one.

197
00:10:36,500 --> 00:10:38,563
Yang Yang, come on. Let's cheers.

198
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:46,781
If you don't eat you won't be full.

199
00:10:56,705 --> 00:10:58,572
Yang Yang,

200
00:10:59,445 --> 00:11:01,545
I think

201
00:11:01,545 --> 00:11:04,305
you're not treating me like your brother.

202
00:11:04,305 --> 00:11:05,705
Why should I treat you like my brother?

203
00:11:05,705 --> 00:11:07,740
Because you call me "Brother Bin" all the time.

204
00:11:07,740 --> 00:11:10,485
If you're not willing to call me "Dad", then we should

205
00:11:10,485 --> 00:11:12,098
just treat each other like buddies.

206
00:11:12,098 --> 00:11:13,705
That's fine.

207
00:11:13,705 --> 00:11:15,454
But,

208
00:11:16,185 --> 00:11:18,166
shouldn't buddies

209
00:11:18,166 --> 00:11:21,325
be honest with each other?

210
00:11:21,325 --> 00:11:24,126
How can you leave without a word?

211
00:11:24,126 --> 00:11:26,986
Don't be obsessed about going to Beijing to see your mom.

212
00:11:26,986 --> 00:11:28,905
Are you a tadpole looking for your mom all the time?

213
00:11:28,905 --> 00:11:30,460
No, I'm not.

214
00:11:30,460 --> 00:11:33,740
- I'm going to see Wang Cailing, okay?
- See, I was right.

215
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,626
I know you too well.

216
00:11:35,626 --> 00:11:37,785
I just signed you up for cram school

217
00:11:37,785 --> 00:11:39,780
and held you up from reuniting with your mom.

218
00:11:39,780 --> 00:11:41,866
That's why you're holding a grudge.

219
00:11:41,866 --> 00:11:44,640
But you can't just cause a scene on the train.

220
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:47,065
Who was the one that caused a scene on the train?

221
00:11:47,065 --> 00:11:48,846
If you didn't stop me, I would be at Tiananmen already.

222
00:11:48,846 --> 00:11:50,585
Why do you want to go to Tiananmen?

223
00:11:50,585 --> 00:11:52,866
Would people in the capital give you food or drinks?

224
00:11:52,866 --> 00:11:55,405
Do you think you're a stinkhorn that can grow with a bit of water?

225
00:11:55,405 --> 00:11:58,165
- You're going to see your mom after all...
- So what if I'm going to see my mom? She's my mom!

226
00:11:58,165 --> 00:11:59,986
How is your mom better than me?

227
00:11:59,986 --> 00:12:01,321
Sure, she's rich.

228
00:12:01,321 --> 00:12:03,220
She can buy you cell phones and brand-name items.

229
00:12:03,220 --> 00:12:04,440
But is that love?

230
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:07,309
If she really loves you, why doesn't she come back to visit you?

231
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,506
You have quite a temper now, huh?

232
00:12:11,506 --> 00:12:12,900
Should I call you "Dad"

233
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:15,121
and bow to you?

234
00:12:19,006 --> 00:12:20,734
There's no need.

235
00:12:38,065 --> 00:12:39,676
Wipe your mouth.

236
00:12:58,103 --> 00:12:59,718
What are you doing?

237
00:13:00,480 --> 00:13:02,598
Don't you love your mom?

238
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,820
These are your favorite sneakers.

239
00:13:04,820 --> 00:13:07,528
She bought them for you. Put them on.

240
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:09,320
Give me my phone then.

241
00:13:09,320 --> 00:13:11,000
No cellphones. Focus on your studies.

242
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:14,146
- Give it to me.
- I said I won't.

243
00:13:14,146 --> 00:13:16,312
Forget about the shoes.

244
00:13:20,034 --> 00:13:22,205
You're slamming the door?

245
00:13:22,205 --> 00:13:24,720
Do you think I want to talk to you?

246
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,660
What the hell?

247
00:13:39,106 --> 00:13:41,420
Gao Yang, answer the phone.

248
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:43,102
No!

249
00:13:43,102 --> 00:13:45,466
Gao Yang, answer the phone.

250
00:13:45,466 --> 00:13:48,326
Gao Yang, answer the phone!

251
00:13:48,326 --> 00:13:51,275
She's asking you to answer the phone!

252
00:13:56,190 --> 00:13:57,340
[2005 Beijing Traffic Tour Guide]

253
00:14:03,663 --> 00:14:04,740
What?

254
00:14:04,740 --> 00:14:06,446
What are you doing?

255
00:14:06,446 --> 00:14:07,705
Nothing.

256
00:14:07,705 --> 00:14:10,600
Then come upstairs, let's play Pupu Push together.

257
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:12,305
I'm not going.

258
00:14:13,580 --> 00:14:17,026
Are you upset because Wang Cailing didn't send you a postcard?

259
00:14:17,026 --> 00:14:20,692
I'm so upset, I wish I could go see her now.

260
00:14:20,692 --> 00:14:23,185
Gao Yang! I have to put some sense in you.
[Jin Beibei,]

261
00:14:23,185 --> 00:14:24,626
You're only seventeen.
[I'm fine in Beijing. Wang Cailing.]

262
00:14:24,626 --> 00:14:26,500
You can't go down the wrong path.

263
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:29,665
I didn't agree when Wang Cailing sat next to you in class!

264
00:14:29,665 --> 00:14:31,606
That really affected your grades!

265
00:14:31,606 --> 00:14:35,166
Is there still room for my grades to drop?

266
00:14:35,166 --> 00:14:36,665
But...

267
00:14:36,665 --> 00:14:38,258
Hello?

268
00:14:49,386 --> 00:14:51,505
Gao Yang!

269
00:14:51,505 --> 00:14:53,585
Time for school, Gao Yang!

270
00:14:53,585 --> 00:14:55,297
Stop yelling.

271
00:14:56,685 --> 00:14:58,160
Good morning, Uncle Gao.

272
00:14:58,160 --> 00:14:59,787
Beibei.

273
00:15:01,689 --> 00:15:03,466
The school is this way!

274
00:15:03,466 --> 00:15:04,825
You go ahead.

275
00:15:04,825 --> 00:15:06,747
Why? Do you want to skip school?

276
00:15:06,747 --> 00:15:08,140
It depends on my mood.

277
00:15:08,140 --> 00:15:10,330
Are you asking for a beating?

278
00:15:12,305 --> 00:15:14,725
Don't be late!

279
00:15:22,977 --> 00:15:24,820
Beibei, you have to make it up soon.

280
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,966
Mr. Wu said he won't accept the homework if I don't collect all of them.

281
00:15:26,966 --> 00:15:29,366
Beibei, there's a new transfer student in our class.

282
00:15:29,366 --> 00:15:30,705
So what?

283
00:15:30,705 --> 00:15:32,816
She's really pretty too.

284
00:15:34,740 --> 00:15:37,306
But far less pretty than you.

285
00:15:37,306 --> 00:15:39,185
Meng, you saw her too?

286
00:15:39,185 --> 00:15:42,020
Yes, she is really pretty.

287
00:15:42,020 --> 00:15:44,764
She sort of looks like Joey Wong.
(T/N: Famous actress known in Hong Kong movies)

288
00:15:57,525 --> 00:15:59,140
I have to sit next to Gao Yang soon.

289
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:01,146
- Sorry, Meng.
- Move where?

290
00:16:01,146 --> 00:16:02,300
Aren't you always sitting by yourself?

291
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:04,060
I'll sit next to you and keep you company.

292
00:16:04,060 --> 00:16:06,026
No, that won't work.

293
00:16:06,026 --> 00:16:09,206
If we sit together, our grades would plummet.

294
00:16:09,206 --> 00:16:10,797
How would that work?

295
00:16:10,797 --> 00:16:11,940
You're right.

296
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:14,785
Jiabao, do you want to sit next to me?

297
00:16:14,785 --> 00:16:15,905
Sure.

298
00:16:15,905 --> 00:16:18,117
Do my homework for me.

299
00:16:19,846 --> 00:16:22,380
- He didn't write anything...
- Meng, that Joey Wong,

300
00:16:22,380 --> 00:16:24,460
how is she compared to Wang Cailing?

301
00:16:24,460 --> 00:16:28,146
Wang Cailing is like a little girl.

302
00:16:28,146 --> 00:16:31,185
But that Joey Wong... is a goddess.

303
00:16:31,185 --> 00:16:33,226
What Joey Wong?

304
00:16:35,801 --> 00:16:37,460
We're talking about...

305
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:39,307
My Sassy Girl.

306
00:16:39,940 --> 00:16:41,991
My Sassy Girl?

307
00:16:43,825 --> 00:16:45,489
Is that right, Jiabao?

308
00:16:47,386 --> 00:16:49,403
My Sassy Girl.

309
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:58,897
Do you still want the money I owe you?

310
00:17:01,421 --> 00:17:04,205
There's a new transfer student in our class. She looks like Joey Wong.

311
00:17:04,205 --> 00:17:06,666
Does she really look like Joey Wong?

312
00:17:06,666 --> 00:17:08,430
Where? Why haven't I seen her?

313
00:17:08,430 --> 00:17:10,065
Mr. Wu's office.

314
00:17:10,065 --> 00:17:11,900
- Zhao Jiabao!
- Move.

315
00:17:11,900 --> 00:17:13,785
I haven't finished yet!

316
00:17:13,785 --> 00:17:15,558
Wait!

317
00:17:15,558 --> 00:17:16,865
What's her name?

318
00:17:16,865 --> 00:17:18,947
I think it's...

319
00:17:21,105 --> 00:17:23,053
Ye Xiaowen.

320
00:17:23,053 --> 00:17:26,192
Ye Xiaowen?

321
00:17:26,192 --> 00:17:30,713
That goes so well with Gao Yang.

322
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:33,860
[Office]

323
00:17:33,860 --> 00:17:36,192
My name is Wu Dibao.

324
00:17:36,192 --> 00:17:37,785
I'm the Grade Leader.

325
00:17:37,785 --> 00:17:40,286
I also teach Chinese Language for your class.

326
00:17:40,286 --> 00:17:42,506
Now that you're at 3rd High School, just think of it as your home.

327
00:17:42,506 --> 00:17:44,120
If you have any problems or any trouble,

328
00:17:44,120 --> 00:17:47,345
tell your class advisor or me at any time, okay?

329
00:17:47,345 --> 00:17:50,197
Mr. Wu, I'm here to turn in the homework!

330
00:18:21,886 --> 00:18:23,986
What are you staring for?

331
00:18:23,986 --> 00:18:25,145
Put it here!

332
00:18:25,145 --> 00:18:27,857
Where's the Study Monitor? Did Tian Meng quit?

333
00:18:27,857 --> 00:18:29,625
Mr. Wu, I've made a decision.

334
00:18:29,625 --> 00:18:33,333
I will study hard and strive to take her place.

335
00:18:33,333 --> 00:18:35,046
See you later, Classmate. I'm leaving now.

336
00:18:35,046 --> 00:18:36,902
Go, go.

337
00:18:38,466 --> 00:18:41,822
Just ignore him. He's really naughty.

338
00:18:45,646 --> 00:18:47,366
Gao Yang,

339
00:18:47,366 --> 00:18:48,955
how nice of you.

340
00:18:48,955 --> 00:18:51,860
You're making it so clean. My pants haven't been washed for 2 weeks.

341
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:54,426
- Wait, what are you doing?
- What's the matter?

342
00:18:54,426 --> 00:18:57,877
This is the seat I saved for our new classmate.

343
00:18:57,877 --> 00:18:59,666
You're making girls more important than friends.

344
00:18:59,666 --> 00:19:01,545
Who's making girls more important than friends?

345
00:19:01,545 --> 00:19:03,746
I'm just afraid you'll affect my grades.

346
00:19:03,746 --> 00:19:05,105
Go back to your own seat.

347
00:19:05,105 --> 00:19:06,847
Pay me back, then.

348
00:19:07,806 --> 00:19:09,260
Jiabao.

349
00:19:09,260 --> 00:19:11,174
Time for class. Hurry, hurry.

350
00:19:11,174 --> 00:19:12,660
Go.

351
00:19:12,660 --> 00:19:15,158
Be good. Stop being fussy.

352
00:19:18,780 --> 00:19:20,145
You just have to come in at the last minute.

353
00:19:20,145 --> 00:19:22,745
Can't you come in earlier?

354
00:19:22,745 --> 00:19:24,205
I have an announcement to make.

355
00:19:24,205 --> 00:19:26,065
In a little while, a new student

356
00:19:26,065 --> 00:19:28,226
will join our class.

357
00:19:28,226 --> 00:19:29,925
Make sure to keep your spirits high

358
00:19:29,925 --> 00:19:32,406
and show her the enthusiasm of Class 3.

359
00:19:32,406 --> 00:19:34,825
Mr. Wu, invite the new classmate in.

360
00:19:34,825 --> 00:19:36,326
She's been waiting for a long time.

361
00:19:36,326 --> 00:19:37,606
Sit down!

362
00:19:37,606 --> 00:19:38,865
You've been acting strange this morning.

363
00:19:38,865 --> 00:19:40,725
Did you take the wrong medicine?

364
00:19:40,725 --> 00:19:43,202
No, I...

365
00:19:45,798 --> 00:19:46,706
I just...

366
00:19:46,706 --> 00:19:50,253
feel lonely for sitting alone all this time.

367
00:19:50,946 --> 00:19:52,540
Keep feeling lonely then!

368
00:19:52,540 --> 00:19:54,216
Come on in.

369
00:20:06,180 --> 00:20:10,260
This is Ye Xiaowen. Come on, Xiaowen. Introduce yourself to everyone.

370
00:20:10,260 --> 00:20:12,385
Why is he a boy?

371
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:16,545
Hello, Everyone. My name is Ye Xiaowen.

372
00:20:17,385 --> 00:20:19,840
He's so aloof and reserved.

373
00:20:19,840 --> 00:20:21,542
Welcome!

374
00:20:25,445 --> 00:20:29,400
Gao Yang, move that desk to the front. Just cope with it up front for a while.

375
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:32,940
It's all right, Mr. Wu. I'll just sit there.

376
00:20:32,940 --> 00:20:34,660
No, that won't be okay, Mr. Wu.

377
00:20:34,660 --> 00:20:39,300
Well, this seat is reserved for Zhao Jiabao.

378
00:20:39,306 --> 00:20:43,925
He has poor eyesight. He can see better if he sits here.

379
00:20:43,925 --> 00:20:46,906
Mr. Wu, he's lying. I have great eyesight.

380
00:20:46,906 --> 00:20:49,704
- Don't interrupt me.
- Stop it!

381
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:55,146
Are you sure you want to sit there? That boy is really naughty. Think about it again.

382
00:20:55,146 --> 00:20:56,445
I'm sure.

383
00:20:56,445 --> 00:20:58,086
Why must he sit over there?

384
00:20:58,086 --> 00:20:59,785
Go sit with your new classmate.

385
00:20:59,785 --> 00:21:02,065
I was just kidding. I saved the seat for you.

386
00:21:02,065 --> 00:21:06,045
All right, just go sit over there. Let me know if he's disturbing you.

387
00:21:06,045 --> 00:21:10,066
Go back to your seat! Class already started and you're still strolling around!

388
00:21:12,000 --> 00:21:14,746
I'm telling you, I'll punish you if you disrupt other students!

389
00:21:14,746 --> 00:21:16,906
I might disrupt them.

390
00:21:16,906 --> 00:21:23,085
Open your books. Class begins. We'll talk about Shakespeare's Hamlet today.

391
00:21:23,085 --> 00:21:25,751
Who are you? Do I know you?

392
00:21:27,385 --> 00:21:29,209
Time for class.

393
00:21:32,310 --> 00:21:35,080
[Wisdom, Enthusiasm, and Diligence]

394
00:21:44,566 --> 00:21:47,524
Stop studying, Meng. Let's eat.

395
00:22:06,420 --> 00:22:09,565
So, you're Ye Xiaowen?

396
00:22:09,565 --> 00:22:11,105
Yes.

397
00:22:11,105 --> 00:22:13,196
Aren't you a boy?

398
00:22:14,326 --> 00:22:16,060
I am a boy.

399
00:22:16,060 --> 00:22:18,825
Then what about that girl? The one in the office.

400
00:22:18,825 --> 00:22:20,592
Who?

401
00:22:20,592 --> 00:22:24,045
The one that looks like this with long legs and long hair.

402
00:22:24,045 --> 00:22:25,620
Mi Jia?

403
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:27,345
Her name is Mi Jia?

404
00:22:27,345 --> 00:22:29,321
She transferred to Class 2.

405
00:22:36,360 --> 00:22:38,778
Rejected.

406
00:22:38,778 --> 00:22:40,602
I'm rejected.

407
00:22:43,086 --> 00:22:47,065
But why are you sitting next to me? Do you know me?

408
00:22:47,065 --> 00:22:49,033
Yes.

409
00:22:55,800 --> 00:23:00,860
Am I that famous now? Even students from another school know me.

410
00:23:00,860 --> 00:23:07,126
Bro, since you sought refuge with me, as the leader of 3rd High school, I won't let you lose your pride.

411
00:23:07,126 --> 00:23:09,506
The rule is first come, first serve.

412
00:23:09,506 --> 00:23:13,086
Do you see that poodle over there? His name is Zhao Jiabao.

413
00:23:13,086 --> 00:23:16,605
He wants to change seats with you. Change seats with him.

414
00:23:16,605 --> 00:23:18,426
That's all right.

415
00:23:18,426 --> 00:23:19,886
What do you mean?

416
00:23:19,886 --> 00:23:22,679
I'll just sit next to you.

417
00:23:22,679 --> 00:23:24,885
Why do you want to sit next to me?

418
00:23:24,885 --> 00:23:26,927
Communicate and improve our friendship.

419
00:23:32,100 --> 00:23:36,206
A sentimental person, huh? Fine. Well, let's talk then.

420
00:23:36,206 --> 00:23:38,717
Which school did you go to?

421
00:23:39,946 --> 00:23:42,138
You've never heard of it.

422
00:23:43,065 --> 00:23:45,121
Where are you from?

423
00:23:45,121 --> 00:23:46,606
You don't need to know.

424
00:23:46,606 --> 00:23:48,728
Are you crazy?

425
00:23:48,728 --> 00:23:51,530
You said communicate and improve our friendship, then answer my questions properly.

426
00:23:51,530 --> 00:23:53,990
Hey, I'm talking to you.

427
00:24:00,070 --> 00:24:01,980
Joey Wong.

428
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:04,730
Do you want to talk to me?

429
00:24:07,666 --> 00:24:09,721
Wait, what's going on?

430
00:24:14,620 --> 00:24:17,246
Go back. Isn't it supposed to be a girl?

431
00:24:17,246 --> 00:24:18,646
What's going on?

432
00:24:18,646 --> 00:24:20,375
What happened?

433
00:24:21,910 --> 00:24:24,050
This question...

434
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:25,525
Can you please explain to me?

435
00:24:25,525 --> 00:24:28,957
You copied this from the physics exam.

436
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:35,426
Stop looking. I'm still here.

437
00:24:35,426 --> 00:24:37,180
Where?

438
00:24:40,210 --> 00:24:41,295
You!

439
00:24:41,295 --> 00:24:42,880
Ye, want some snacks?

440
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,485
Go clean the blackboard.

441
00:24:44,485 --> 00:24:47,066
No, I don't want any.

442
00:24:47,066 --> 00:24:52,066
What are we? We are desk mates now. What's mine is yours.

443
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:57,500
Are you studying? Well, eat while you study.

444
00:24:58,790 --> 00:25:02,666
You and Mi Jia came from the same school, right?

445
00:25:04,683 --> 00:25:09,121
You two seem to have an extraordinary temperament. You must come from a big city.

446
00:25:09,121 --> 00:25:12,280
Is it Linyang? Here's the thing.

447
00:25:12,280 --> 00:25:16,760
Although our Tieyuan is a small place, the people here are really enthusiastic. Am I right, Beibei?

448
00:25:19,920 --> 00:25:24,246
- If you need anything, just tell me. I'll take care of it for you.
- I don't need anything.

449
00:25:24,246 --> 00:25:28,961
What about Mi Jia? Does she need anything? The two of you seem pretty close.

450
00:25:28,961 --> 00:25:32,626
One of you is in Class 2 and the other is in Class 3. It's so inconvenient for you to communicate.

451
00:25:32,626 --> 00:25:36,346
Why don't you ask Mi Jia to transfer to our class?

452
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:40,825
How?

453
00:25:40,825 --> 00:25:47,126
To be honest, I have a special relationship with the principal.

454
00:25:47,126 --> 00:25:48,726
Am I right?

455
00:25:51,226 --> 00:25:53,576
My words count.

456
00:25:54,886 --> 00:25:58,126
That's all right. I don't want to be in the same class with her.

457
00:25:58,126 --> 00:25:59,980
Did you have a fight? That's great.

458
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:04,700
If you need anything, I'll go tell her for you.

459
00:26:04,700 --> 00:26:08,040
I don't know her very well. You don't need to tell her anything.

460
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:13,380
Isn't this Mi Jia's notebook?

461
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:15,220
Little strawberries...

462
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,725
And you're saying you don't know her very well.

463
00:26:16,725 --> 00:26:19,065
What does that have to do with you?

464
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:26,399
He has quite the personality.

465
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:30,345
Do you think she looks like Joey Wong?

466
00:26:30,345 --> 00:26:31,965
I think she looks like Jun Ji-hyun.

467
00:26:31,965 --> 00:26:34,485
She's really pretty.

468
00:26:34,485 --> 00:26:36,647
Her nose is so... Her eyes...

469
00:26:39,926 --> 00:26:42,045
I made all the notes on your notebook.

470
00:26:42,045 --> 00:26:43,812
Thank you.

471
00:26:44,860 --> 00:26:46,330
Here

472
00:26:49,366 --> 00:26:51,085
What's wrong?

473
00:26:55,266 --> 00:26:57,146
Nothing.

474
00:27:00,606 --> 00:27:03,738
Make sure to tell me if you're feeling uncomfortable at all.

475
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:13,086
They... Someone asked me where I came from.

476
00:27:13,086 --> 00:27:14,385
What did you say?

477
00:27:14,385 --> 00:27:16,746
I... I just ignored them.

478
00:27:16,746 --> 00:27:18,797
Haven't I taught you what to say?

479
00:27:19,926 --> 00:27:22,182
I'm afraid I'll spill the beans.

480
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:30,966
You still have to practice. You have to communicate with other people eventually.

481
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:38,245
What about you? Did you see Gao Yang?

482
00:27:38,245 --> 00:27:40,558
What is he like?

483
00:27:42,126 --> 00:27:46,106
I don't know him very well. Just ignore him when you see him later.

484
00:27:46,920 --> 00:27:48,653
I'm heading back now.

485
00:27:52,980 --> 00:27:55,585
- Go ahead, be arrogant now.
- Gao Yang!

486
00:27:55,585 --> 00:27:56,725
- Gao Yang!
- What's wrong?

487
00:27:56,725 --> 00:27:57,706
- Let go of me!
- No, I won't.

488
00:27:57,706 --> 00:28:00,160
- Let go of me!
- What if I won't?

489
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:04,480
Tell me, what do you like about Gao Yang?

490
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:10,025
How do I explain it? We grew up together. It's sort of a responsibility.

491
00:28:10,741 --> 00:28:11,466
How great of you.

492
00:28:11,466 --> 00:28:13,978
- It's just a chicken drumstick. Is it a big deal?
- I just can't let you off easy!

493
00:28:13,978 --> 00:28:15,297
I won't lend you money next time!

494
00:28:15,297 --> 00:28:17,345
Well, don't hide your DVDs at my house!

495
00:28:17,345 --> 00:28:19,292
Fine, I won't then!

496
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:23,365
Do you know how awful Gao Bin's cooking is? I'm counting on lunch!

497
00:28:23,365 --> 00:28:24,740
- So what?
- What do you think?

498
00:28:24,740 --> 00:28:26,560
Enough! Stop yelling.

499
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:28,660
- It's just a chicken drumstick.
- Exactly.

500
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:30,026
Come to dinner at my place.

501
00:28:30,026 --> 00:28:31,806
No, I'm not going. Your dad always lectures me.

502
00:28:31,806 --> 00:28:34,437
- He's doing that for your own good!
- What are you talking about?

503
00:28:35,540 --> 00:28:37,606
How can you talk so loudly in school?

504
00:28:37,606 --> 00:28:39,445
Hello, Schoolmate.

505
00:28:40,065 --> 00:28:42,245
Are you Mi Jia?

506
00:28:42,245 --> 00:28:47,065
I'm Gao Yang from Class Three. Your former classmate Ye Xiaowen is currently my deskmate.

507
00:28:47,065 --> 00:28:48,946
She does look really pretty.

508
00:28:48,946 --> 00:28:51,030
No, she's not.

509
00:28:51,030 --> 00:28:54,826
Gao... Yang?

510
00:28:54,826 --> 00:28:56,659
She knows me!

511
00:28:57,226 --> 00:28:59,109
Let's be friends.

512
00:29:03,220 --> 00:29:05,520
Gao Yang, you have quite the reputation.

513
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:08,245
When girls from other classes see you, they'll all become long-distance.

514
00:29:08,245 --> 00:29:10,666
Gao Yang, I didn't expect people to despise you so much.

515
00:29:10,666 --> 00:29:14,585
Who knows? Let's go. Don't let the wind ruin your handsome hairstyle.

516
00:29:14,585 --> 00:29:17,769
- Let's go back to class!
- She's just shy.

517
00:29:19,445 --> 00:29:24,306
Ye Xiaowen, it must be his fault.

518
00:29:33,900 --> 00:29:36,290
Ye Xiaowen, you're quite something.

519
00:29:36,290 --> 00:29:39,920
I treated you like my buddy and you ruined my reputation out there!

520
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:44,080
No, no. Hurts, it hurts.

521
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,417
What are you talking about?

522
00:29:45,417 --> 00:29:50,526
You know what I'm talking about. I hate two-faced bast*rds!

523
00:29:50,526 --> 00:29:55,517
Let me tell you, don't leave after school. I'll see you on the balcony. Do you hear me?

524
00:29:55,517 --> 00:29:58,105
You should go home after school.

525
00:30:02,620 --> 00:30:04,880
You don't seem to understand.

526
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:06,786
I, Gao Yang, want to compete with you

527
00:30:06,786 --> 00:30:10,826
and show you what Gao from No. 3 High School is made of! Do you hear me?

528
00:30:10,826 --> 00:30:12,499
Let me see what you're made of.

529
00:30:12,499 --> 00:30:13,980
Mr. Wu, I need to use the toilet.

530
00:30:13,980 --> 00:30:18,806
What do you mean you need to use the toilet? Get down from there! Stand right here!

531
00:30:18,806 --> 00:30:20,110
You think you're so tough, huh?

532
00:30:20,110 --> 00:30:22,797
What the hell are you doing? Why are you bullying him on his first day?

533
00:30:22,797 --> 00:30:24,585
- I didn't.
- Shut up!

534
00:30:24,585 --> 00:30:28,095
How will other people think of No. 3 High School and our Class Three? Come out here!

535
00:30:28,095 --> 00:30:30,140
No, Mr. Wu. You didn't wash your hands yet!

536
00:30:30,140 --> 00:30:31,653
Why should I? I haven't started yet!

537
00:30:31,653 --> 00:30:34,100
- But it will smell...
- Mr. Wu.

538
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:36,266
Stop! Stand right there!

539
00:30:38,560 --> 00:30:42,308
Uncle Zhang. Uncle Li, you're here too? Auntie Yang, you look even younger again.

540
00:30:42,308 --> 00:30:45,100
Stop showing off! Is this your family reunion?

541
00:30:45,100 --> 00:30:48,000
I'm telling you, you were out of line! I won't let you off easy!

542
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:53,380
It's no big deal. Well, Uncles, Aunties, Teachers, you have all watched us grow up.

543
00:30:53,380 --> 00:30:55,785
You know who I am. Would I really beat him up?

544
00:30:55,785 --> 00:30:58,260
I was just intimidating him.

545
00:30:58,260 --> 00:31:01,740
I'll apologize to everyone. Let's just leave it like that.

546
00:31:01,740 --> 00:31:04,132
Mr. Wu, I'm leaving now.

547
00:31:04,132 --> 00:31:05,734
Stop right there!

548
00:31:07,793 --> 00:31:11,625
I'm telling you, Gao Yang. We can reprimand you for your dad over other matters.

549
00:31:11,625 --> 00:31:14,090
But bullying Ye Xiaowen is a serious matter. Do you understand that?

550
00:31:14,090 --> 00:31:15,740
I didn't bully him.

551
00:31:15,740 --> 00:31:17,357
Sir.

552
00:31:18,580 --> 00:31:20,993
You're here right in time. Come here.

553
00:31:23,666 --> 00:31:25,006
Xiaowen, let me tell you

554
00:31:25,006 --> 00:31:26,520
this boy is just a unique case.

555
00:31:26,520 --> 00:31:30,060
All the other classmates and teachers really welcome you here. Don't take it to heart.

556
00:31:30,060 --> 00:31:31,680
Mr. Wu,

557
00:31:31,680 --> 00:31:34,059
Gao Yang didn't do anything to me.

558
00:31:35,245 --> 00:31:37,637
Look at him and look at you!

559
00:31:39,245 --> 00:31:41,666
All right, you can go now. We'll handle his incident.

560
00:31:41,666 --> 00:31:44,120
He really didn't do anything to me.

561
00:31:44,120 --> 00:31:46,420
All right, I've heard you. Go on now.

562
00:31:48,765 --> 00:31:50,637
Wait a minute.

563
00:31:54,180 --> 00:31:58,131
I... I've prepared something for you. It's just a welcome gift.

564
00:31:58,131 --> 00:32:01,580
- Mr. Wu, you really don't have to.
- Just take it.

565
00:32:01,580 --> 00:32:03,727
Take it.

566
00:32:03,727 --> 00:32:08,365
All right, tell me if you need anything.

567
00:32:09,220 --> 00:32:12,232
- Thank you, Mr. Wu.
- It's okay. Go on.

568
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,426
Mr. Wu, what's his background?

569
00:32:20,426 --> 00:32:23,925
What does that have to do with you? Tell me, what should I do about this?

570
00:32:24,860 --> 00:32:27,145
Well, I'll write a self-criticism.

571
00:32:27,145 --> 00:32:28,620
Writing a self-criticism is hard work.

572
00:32:28,620 --> 00:32:30,240
Isn't it?

573
00:32:31,026 --> 00:32:32,817
How about this? Let's do Plan A.

574
00:32:32,817 --> 00:32:36,335
That's too harsh. I won't be able to carry myself in school.

575
00:32:36,335 --> 00:32:38,700
- It is a bit harsh.
- Exactly.

576
00:32:38,700 --> 00:32:39,946
Plan A it is then.

577
00:32:39,946 --> 00:32:43,226
Mr. Wu, why don't we forget about it. Let's not do this.

578
00:32:43,226 --> 00:32:47,245
Where's that spirit of yours back there? Now you're feeling embarrassed. Sing, hurry up.

579
00:32:47,245 --> 00:32:50,620
Mr. Wu, please cut Gao Yang some slack.

580
00:32:50,620 --> 00:32:53,146
Cut him what slack? You two, sing together.

581
00:32:53,146 --> 00:32:55,406
Jiabao will sing. He's a good singer.

582
00:32:55,406 --> 00:32:57,020
Jin Beibei, you're too much!

583
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:58,700
The three of you will sing together.

584
00:32:58,700 --> 00:33:00,748
Gao Yang, just sing.

585
00:33:02,440 --> 00:33:05,283
Sing! Hurry up!

586
00:33:05,283 --> 00:33:10,310
♪ The rain is pouring ♪

587
00:33:10,310 --> 00:33:12,280
Louder!

588
00:33:13,485 --> 00:33:15,075
Sing!

589
00:33:15,766 --> 00:33:19,925
♪ The rain is pouring. Oh, yeah ♪

590
00:33:19,925 --> 00:33:21,765
You're so off-key.

591
00:33:21,765 --> 00:33:23,865
Don't just sing. Add some moves to it.

592
00:33:23,865 --> 00:33:28,985
Show everyone the arrogant manner you used to carry yourself with. Start dancing. Come on.

593
00:33:28,985 --> 00:33:30,480
Stop looking. Stop looking!

594
00:33:30,480 --> 00:33:32,440
Why are you not going home after school? You've never seen pretty girls before?

595
00:33:32,440 --> 00:33:34,706
- Stop looking. Go home!
- Go home! Go home!

596
00:33:34,706 --> 00:33:37,500
Are they looking at you? Why are you being so pretentious?

597
00:33:38,466 --> 00:33:40,785
Sing. Why did you stop?

598
00:33:40,785 --> 00:33:42,462
I...

599
00:33:43,746 --> 00:33:45,345
I lost my voice, Mr. Wu.

600
00:33:45,345 --> 00:33:50,286
Mr. Wu, you're lecturing your student? See you tomorrow.

601
00:33:50,286 --> 00:33:52,460
Bin, it's your son.

602
00:33:52,460 --> 00:33:55,086
Thanks. Discipline him!

603
00:33:57,426 --> 00:34:01,226
♪ Every face is ridden with resign ♪

604
00:34:01,226 --> 00:34:04,225
♪ My parents don't love each other ♪

605
00:34:07,646 --> 00:34:13,125
All right, Gao Yang. Just think of it as your solo concert in school.

606
00:34:13,125 --> 00:34:14,500
You're making fun of me?

607
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:16,346
No.

608
00:34:16,346 --> 00:34:18,330
How about this? Look on the bright side.

609
00:34:18,330 --> 00:34:22,350
Everyone in school knows you now. You're famous.

610
00:34:26,130 --> 00:34:30,860
There's good fame and bad fame. I don't want to be famous this way. You could do it if you want.

611
00:34:35,026 --> 00:34:39,365
Gao Yang, I'll be honest with you. Don't be upset when you hear it.

612
00:34:39,365 --> 00:34:44,065
I think Ye Xiaowen is pretty nice. You really shouldn't do that to him.

613
00:34:44,065 --> 00:34:45,806
What?

614
00:34:45,806 --> 00:34:47,506
Even you fell under his spell?

615
00:34:47,506 --> 00:34:49,105
No.

616
00:34:49,105 --> 00:34:54,285
That Ye Xiaowen is not a good boy. He even fooled the teachers in school.

617
00:34:55,145 --> 00:35:00,080
Jin Beibei, from now on, the two of us will be archenemies in school.

618
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:03,026
Don't let me see you come in any contact with him.

619
00:35:03,026 --> 00:35:06,285
Otherwise, that will be the end of our friendship. Do you hear me?

620
00:35:06,285 --> 00:35:11,165
Gao Yang, why are you so petty?

621
00:35:18,346 --> 00:35:20,866
Making dinner again, Gao Bin?

622
00:35:20,866 --> 00:35:26,745
I'm telling you, your cooking is really inedible. Just cook some instant noodles.

623
00:35:29,140 --> 00:35:32,200
Smells pretty good. What are you making?

624
00:35:35,065 --> 00:35:38,720
You're home? Dinner will be ready soon.

625
00:35:40,366 --> 00:35:42,434
Why are you at my house?

626
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:14,535
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

627
00:36:14,535 --> 00:36:21,598
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

628
00:36:21,598 --> 00:36:27,888
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

629
00:36:27,888 --> 00:36:33,928
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

630
00:36:33,928 --> 00:36:40,480
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

631
00:36:40,480 --> 00:36:46,220
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

632
00:36:46,220 --> 00:36:50,107
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

633
00:36:50,107 --> 00:36:53,555
♫  Let set sail on our dreams  ♫

634
00:36:53,555 --> 00:36:56,850
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

635
00:36:56,850 --> 00:37:03,510
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

636
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:06,921
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

637
00:37:06,921 --> 00:37:10,933
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

638
00:37:10,933 --> 00:37:14,753
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

639
00:37:14,753 --> 00:37:21,013
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
